      • getNodeForResource

        public static DepTreeNode getNodeForResource(URI requestUri,
                             Map<URI,DepTreeNode> dependencies)
        Maps a resource URI to a DepTreeNode. This routine finds the key in dependencies that is an ancestor of requiestURI and then looks for the DepTreeNode who's name corresponds to descendant part of the URI path.
        Parameters:
        requestUri - The URI for the resource location being sought
        dependencies - Map of file path names to root DepTreeNodes
        Returns:
        The node corresponding to requestURI

      • parseDependencies

        public static ArrayList<String> parseDependencies(com.google.javascript.rhino.Node node)
        Walks the parsed AST Node looking for the AMD define() function call and extracts the require list of dependencies to a string array and returns the buildReader.

        Any require list entries that are not a string literal (e.g. an object ref) are omitted from the returned array.

        Parameters:
        node - A parsed AST Node for a javascript file
        Returns:
        The String array of module dependencies.
